        "Data": [
          "==Applies To==\n\n* PCI DSS Requirement 8.2.4\n\n==Policy Statement==\n\nChange passwords regularly.\n\n==Policy Purpose==\n\nChanging passwords regularly ensures that if a password has been compromised, it will soon become useless.\n\n==Related Guidance==\n\n* [[a3f48e53-b118-4180-8aa1-e945f1afadda|Force Password Renewal]]\n\n==Related Checklist Items==\n\n* [[af1a2a69-bb4d-4ca4-86ab-174c4c5e3ca9|Password Renewal Is Enforced]]"
        ]
